{"tid":2438640,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"自動波/電動車波棍","createTime":"2021-03-08T15:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T03:47:05.000Z","uid":217842,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d70b1c67b8ffb4f6d6783dd3d5dda1f27826f47","tid":2438640,"uid":217842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"事緣呢排睇新車 <br />\n見到Leaf 支「波棍」覺得好撚on9<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4A0qEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4A0qEG.jpg&h=d2b7ab7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又曬位又難用<br />\n<br />\n其實喺自動波甚至電動嘅年代 <br />\n波「棍」到底有無存在意義 <br />\n既然有唔少車都整做制<br />\n<br />\n不如中間整多啲儲物仲好<br />\n四粒膠制嘅成本唔係應該仲低過成支波棍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />波棍根本無必要 PRND 四粒制就得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣車無碌棍渣手唔叫渣車"},{"pid":"34cc53136582a3ce4410f05c7c87226828672d23","tid":2438640,"uid":252789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"自動駕駛啦 仲揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d785aac51796d50abd5c03bc7b81ec09b2283d09","tid":2438640,"uid":13544,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i115.photobucket.com/albums/n318/CW3359/IMG_4726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi115.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fn318%2FCW3359%2FIMG_4726.jpg&h=9512ce4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士用波掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627350afc3a69a9ac23af2b7d6511c399bf73fa0","tid":2438640,"uid":217842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d785aac51796d50abd5c03bc7b81ec09b2283d09","tid":2438640,"uid":13544,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=